model.epanet.element.optionsreport

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.epanet.element.optionsreport.Time

  • public final class Time
extends Object
    This class defines various time step parameters used in the simulation. The format for Duration, Hydraulic Timestep, Quality Timestep, Pattern Timestep, Pattern Start, Report Timestep, Report Start is:

    value (units) 1. Units can be SECONDS (SEC), MINUTES (MIN), HOURS, or DAYS. The default is hours.

    2. If no units are supplied, then time values can be expressed in either decimal hours or in hours:minutes notation.

    The Start ClockTime has the next format: value (AM/PM)

    For example:

     DURATION 240 HOURS
 QUALITY TIMESTEP 3 MIN
 QUALITY TIMESTEP 0:03
 REPORT START 120
 STATISTIC AVERAGE
 START CLOCKTIME 6:00 AM


    Notes:
    The format is not validated
